Which of the following is a container for CloudWatch metrics?

Namespace

A namespace is a container for CloudWatch metrics (e.g., EC2 uses the AWS/EC2 namespace). Metrics in different namespaces are isolated from each other so that metrics from different applications are not mistakenly aggregated into the same statistics.

